  randomFlavorTable:
    title: WHY IS THIS STICK USEFUL?
    columns:
    - header: Use Instantly cools any
      values:
      - liquid it touches Insects hate the smell
      - It transforms into 20ft of rope when shaken
      - Terrifies snakes, eels, and worms
      - One end is extremely sticky
